`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
`8Keywords``   : Punish
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * punish list
 * punish penalties
 * punish <player> <punishment> <#> days|hours|minutes
 * punish remove <player> <punishment>
 * punish previous <player>

 The punish command applies a punishment to a player. A list of punishments can
be obtained with the "penalties" subcommand. The previous punishments a player
has received can be viewed with "punish previous", and a list of all people
currently with punishments can be viewed with "punish list".

`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``
